{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A cozy, dimly lit bedroom scene with a purple-blue ambient glow, inspired by TikTok and Pinterest aesthetics. The environment subtly matches a real-life house interior, but details are blurred slightly to keep a casual and believable look. In the room, a young woman sits casually, her face not fully visible but her features subtly matching the uploaded photos. She looks relaxed, perhaps on her phone. Nearby, there is a blurry figure of a &#x27;friend&#x27; to make it feel natural, like a real candid Snapchat moment. The room has soft blankets, maybe a TV in the background, and an LED light glow, but everything is slightly blurry to maintain a casual vibe without too much sharp detail. Focus on making it look realistic and lowkey, like a real moment captured in low light.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;,
  &quot;transparent_background&quot;: false
}

{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A casual, moody indoor Snapchat-like photo of a young woman with dark hair in a low bun, wearing a light tank top and light jeans, standing casually in a dimly lit room with purple-blue LED ambient lighting. The setting has cozy, slightly messy vibes with a visible ceiling fan, textured walls, and simple decor. She looks relaxed, naturally caught mid-motion. A &#x27;friend&#x27; figure, slightly blurred, is sitting nearby, adding to the chill, candid atmosphere. The image should have a slight grainy filter, resembling a low-light smartphone snap, with soft, imperfect focus, but still recognizable.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;,
  &quot;transparent_background&quot;: false
}

{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;Create an artistic portrait showing how others might perceive a young woman with light skin, dark hair, glasses, a tattoo on her shoulder, and a calm but strong energy. The scene should feel dreamy, slightly ethereal, with soft lighting, a hint of mystery, and an emotional depth. Capture a vibe that blends beauty, intelligence, resilience, and quiet strength. Background should be subtle and a little blurred, suggesting inner depth more than physical surroundings.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;
}
